race.description: Tabtouch Westspeed Platinum Series Heat 3 Handicap
race.comment: AUTO CRUISE (9) looks an exciting horse on the rise, closing off strongly in a CL1 last start at Belmont. Tougher here, but CJP sticks with her and she looks open to plenty of improvement. The slight rise in trip should suit and she can land the knockout blow. THE SPRUIKER (5) missed in a photo finish first-up at Albany over a trip well short of his best. He went in without a trial there and looks well placed coming here now. The inside draw is a big tick and he can end his winning drought today. MOHEGAN RULER (8) closed off strongly last time out and has claims on the back of that effort. GOLD MAKER (2) will appreciate stepping up in trip again now and looks an improver.
